"2  quarts cranberry juice cocktail","8  slices (quarter size and about 1/8 in. thick) peeled fresh ginger","2  cinnamon sticks (about 3 in. long)","2  whole star anise","1/3 cup cognac or brandy","8 cups Champagne or other sparkling wine (about 2 2/3 bottles, 750 ml. each), chilled","32  to 48 fresh cranberries, rinsed, or frozen cranberries (optional)"